  <title>Central Test Data Editor</title>
  <anchor role="helpid" condition="guidancerCentralTestDataEditorContextId" xml:id="central-test-data-editor.guidancerCentralTestDataEditorContextId">Central Test Data</anchor>
  <para>
    You can open the Central Test Data Editor via the button on the
    toolbar.
  </para>
  <para>
    In the Central Test Data Editor:
  </para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        You can create, modify and delete central test data sets.
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        You can search for places where central test data sets have
        been used.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>